st 'cause you don't like darks in the first place doesn't permit you to be a punk. Lighten up and get your fellow lights to stop corpse camping, L&amp;S wouldn't be in debate if people would just leave their kill alone after you kill them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000028><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub7.ezboard.com/uatomobombo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Atomo Bombo</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>   <font color=#FFFF00>(7/14/00 9:13:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub77.ezboard.com/ftallonzektimes4735guildsoftallonzek.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=33.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/atomobombo/gildon.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Progeny of Hate PvP Guidelines</span><hr size=1> We had a little encounter with Skotos (sp?) of PoH in Rathe today, Gildon had killed him in SK, he was bound in Rathe, and while we were there, he attacked us and necro healed other players. We killed him naked, but he would come back and do the same. We told him to leave, but he didn't. I've gotten about 10 DE faction hits from 1 PoH member who didn't want to scoot, and that was in Unrest. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#00000F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub7.ezboard.com/btallonzektimes4735.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=kayramidnight>Kayramidnight</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>   <font color=#FFFF00>(7/15/00 2:47:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub77.ezboard.com/ftallonzektimes4735guildsoftallonzek.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=33.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Progeny of Hate PvP Guidelines</span><hr size=1> Skotos was wrong to do that, however, he was in another zone and made a poor judgement call when he saw your group using invincible healers. He canceled his right to a safe corpse run with his actions. He still should not have been bind camped.<br><br>As for the Unrest incident, it was not brought to me.<br><br>Any problem that arises can be handled in an adult manner without name calling, etc.<br><br>I have seen members of various guilds, HA included, who did not loot n scoot either. Only difference is I do not feel the need to slander anyone playing a game for enjoyment nor corpse camp them.<br><br>~Kayramidnight D'Raklyn~<br>Guild Mistress<br>Progeny of Hate <p></p><i>Edited by <A HREF=http://pub7.ezboard.com/btallonzektimes4735.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=kayramidnight>Kayramidnight</A> at: 7/15/00 3:52:54 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000028><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub7.ezboard.com/uatomobombo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Atomo Bombo</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>   <font color=#FFFF00>(7/15/00 10:10:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub77.ezboard.com/ftallonzektimes4735guildsoftallonzek.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=33.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/atomobombo/gildon.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Progeny of Hate PvP Guidelines</span><hr size=1> He was not bind camped, he was told to leave the zone since he had died in it and refused. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub77.ezboard.com/ftallonzektimes4735guildsoftallonzek.showPrevMessage?topicID=33.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub77.ezboard.com/ftallonzektimes4735guildso